short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Supercharge productivity with our revolutionary tool,seamlessly connecting WhatsApp and Salesforce!

long.ar,bg,bn,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_U: Specifically crafted for your sales and customer support teams, this tool effortlessly syncs your contacts with leads and accounts. Create new records—be it leads, contacts, cases, opportunities, requests, contracts, tasks, events, or notes—directly from WhatsApp. Elevate your workflow by uploading images, videos, and documents straight from WhatsApp Web to your Salesforce records. This tool is your go-to solution for enhancing efficiency and communication synergy between WhatsApp and Salesforce. Transform the way your teams collaborate and streamline processes for unparalleled productivity.

Create new records—be it leads, contacts, cases, opportunities, requests, contracts, tasks, events, or notes—directly from WhatsApp. Elevate your workflow by uploading images, videos, and documents straight from WhatsApp Web to your Salesforce records.
